@theworlds50best has just revealed the 2026 Asia’s 50 Best Restaurants 51–100 list. With exciting new entries like @chef1996restaurant @silkshouse_taipei @fumeerestaurant @cochengdu and standout restaurants like @ta_vie_hk @vea_hk @ando.hkg @amberhongkong in Hong Kong and @ensue_sz @xinrongji_xinyuannanlu in China, the list continues to spotlight the remarkable breadth and creativity of Asian cuisine and its growing global influence. As the official sauce and condiment partner, Lee Kum Kee is proud to stand #BehindTheBest and celebrate the chefs pushing Asian flavors forward on the world stage.

Which restaurant is your pick? Let us know in the comments.

